ansfer costs\n\n**Note:** Requires AWS Cost Explorer API integration or custom cost metrics","background_color":"blue","font_size":"14","text_align":"left","show_tick":false,"tick_pos":"50%","tick_edge":"left","has_padding":true},"layout":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":12,"height":2}},{"id":5010200987755529,"definition":{"title":"🤖 Bedrock Token Usage (Estimated)","show_legend":false,"type":"timeseries","requests":[{"response_format":"timeseries","queries":[{"data_source":"spans","name":"bedrock_calls","compute":{"aggregation":"count"},"search":{"query":"service:$service.value env:$env.value resource_name:*bedrock*"}}],"formulas":[{"formula":"bedrock_calls","alias":"API Calls"}]}]},"layout":{"x":0,"y":2,"width":6,"height":3}},{"id":3676303315994393,"definition":{"title":"Total Bedrock Calls (30d)","type":"query_value","requests":[{"response_format":"scalar","queries":[{"data_source":"spans","name":"total","compute":{"aggregation":"count"},"search":{"query":"service:$service.value env:$env.value resource_name:*bedrock*"}}],"formulas":[{"formula":"total"}]}],"autoscale":true,"precision":0},"layout":{"x":6,"y":2,"width":3,"height":2}},{"id":1824708297304720,"definition":{"title":"Avg Calls per Day","type":"query_value","requests":[{"response_format":"scalar","queries":[{"data_source":"spans","name":"daily","compute":{"aggregation":"count"},"search":{"query":"service:$service.value env:$env.value resource_name:*bedrock*"}}],"formulas":[{"formula":"daily / 30"}]}],"autoscale":true,"precision":0},"layout":{"x":9,"y":2,"width":3,"height":2}},{"id":4592715336264427,"definition":{"title":"Top LLM Models by Usage","type":"toplist","requests":[{"queries":[{"data_source":"spans","name":"models","compute":{"aggregation":"count"},"search":{"query":"service:$service.value env:$env.value resource_name:*bedrock*"},"group_by":[{"facet":"resource_name","limit":10,"sort":{"aggregation":"count","order":"desc"}}]}],"response_format":"scalar","formulas":[{"formula":"models"}],"sort":{"count":10,"order_by":[{"type":"formula","index":0,"order":"desc"}]}}]},"layout":{"x":0,"y":5,"width":12,"height":4}},{"id":5244448644472009,"definition":{"type":"note","content":"**Cost Tracking Setup:**\n\n**Option 1: AWS Cost Explorer API**\n- Integrate AWS Cost Explorer API\n- Tag resources with service/env\n- Send cost metrics to DataDog\n\n**Option 2: Custom Metrics**\n- Track token usage in application\n- Calculate costs based on pricing\n- Send custom metrics: `ai.cost.bedrock`, `ai.cost.tokens`\n\n**Bedrock Pricing (Approximate):**\n- Claude 3 Sonnet: $3/1M input tokens, $15/1M output\n- Claude 3 Haiku: $0.25/1M input, $1.25/1M output\n\n**Note:** Actual costs require instrumentation of token counts from LLM responses","background_color":"yellow","font_size":"14","text_align":"left","show_tick":false,"has_padding":true},"layout":{"x":0,"y":9,"width":12,"height":3}}]},"layout":{"x":0,"y":48,"width":12,"height":13}},{"id":2594354145544860,"definition":{"title":"🔒 Security & Compliance","type":"group","layout_type":"ordered","widgets":[{"id":430341566676095,"definition":{"type":"note","content":"## 🔒 Security & Compliance\n\n**Purpose:** Monitor security events and compliance metrics\n\n**Key Metrics:**\n- Authentication failures\n- Authorization errors\n- Suspicious activity patterns\n- Data access audit logs\n\n**Note:** Requires security event instrumentation and audit logging","background_color":"blue","font_size":"14","text_align":"left","show_tick":false,"tick_pos":"50%","tick_edge":"left","has_padding":true},"layout":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":12,"height":2}},{"id":5959887124941774,"definition":{"title":"🔐 Authentication Errors (401)","show_legend":false,"type":"timeseries","requests":[{"response_format":"timeseries","queries":[{"data_source":"spans","name":"auth_errors","compute":{"aggregation":"count"},"search":{"query":"service:$service.value env:$env.value http.status_code:401"}}],"formulas":[{"formula":"auth_errors","alias":"401 Errors"}]}]},"layout":{"x":0,"y":2,"wid